        <div class="container my-5" id="champions">
            <img src="{{ asset("client/assets/media/media14.png") }}" alt="" width="100%" alt="" style="height: 500px;">
            <h2 class="mt-3">
                Who Will Win the 2025 Champions League?
            </h2>
            <p>
                The 2025 Champions League is shaping up to be one of the most competitive in recent memory, with several teams vying for European glory. Real Madrid, the defending champions, remain favorites. However, they’ll face stiff competition from the likes of Manchester City, Arsenal, Bayern Munich, and other European powerhouses just to name a few.
            </p>
            <p>
                Real Madrid, with their rich history in the competition, can never be counted out. The Spanish giants have won the Champions League a record 14 times, and with players like Vinicius Jr., Jude Bellingham, and potentially Kylian Mbappe in their ranks, they have the firepower to go all the way. Bayern Munich, under the leadership of Thomas Tuchel, also pose a significant threat. Their balanced squad, combining experience and youth, along with their high-pressing, attacking style, makes them one of the most dangerous teams in Europe.
            </p>
            <p>
