            </p>
            <p>
                The streaming model has also influenced the types of stories being told. With the ability to target niche audiences, streaming platforms are more willing to take risks on diverse and unconventional projects that might not have found a place in traditional Hollywood. However, this race for content has also led to concerns about quality control and the sustainability of such high production rates. As the streaming wars continue, the industry will need to navigate the challenges of maintaining creative integrity while meeting the demands of a fast-paced, competitive market.
